                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It struck me - every Day -</l>
                    <l>The Lightning was as new </l>
                    <l>As if the Cloud that instant<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 slit </l>
                    <l>And let the Fire through - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It burned Me - in the Night -</l>
                    <l>It Blistered to My Dream - </l>
                    <l>It sickened fresh opon my<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 sight - </l>
                    <l>With every Morn that came - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I thought that Storm - was brief - </l>
                    <l>The Maddest - quickest by -</l>
                    <l>But Nature lost the Date<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of This - </l>
                    <l>And left it in the Sky - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
